19
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,760
Ça s’appelle la sphère de Hoberman.

20
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:11,240
Voilà le rythme d’expansion et de contraction : expansion, contraction, expansion, contraction.

21
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:17,360
